'''Gurbanguly''' Mälikgulyýewiç '''Berdimuhamedow'''<ref>Yettwaru s sin ''m'' am s [[taturkminit]] (''Berdimuhammedow'') am s trusit (''Бердымухаммедов'') alama d {{azmez|25|yunyu|2007}} (zeṛ ɣef udeg web n ''Radio Free Europe'' [http://www.rferl.org/content/article/1074635.html]), isem n twacult-is yettwaru seg uzmez agi s yiwen ''m'' kan deg iḍrisen unṣben dɣa deg iɣmisen.</ref> (s [[tarusit|trusit]] : Гурбангулы Мяликгулыевич Бердымухамедов, yettwaru aka ''Gourbangouly Mialikgoulyïevitch Berdymoukhamedov'', d talɣa timeẓwit. Ilul ass n [[29 yunyu]] [[1957]]) d aselway n [[Turkministan]]. Yeṭṭfed afrisem n Arkadag (amɛellem  amastan) dɣa yebna [[aɛbad n tugna|aɛbad ines n tugna]]<ref>[[Courrier international]], {{n°|1168}} n 21 ar 27 meɣres 2013, {{p.}}44</ref>.
